Query Language:
manufacuter: manufacturer of the cereal
type: type of cereal, cold or hot
rating: rating of cereal 0-100
shelf: shelf from the floor 1,2,3
potassium: amount of potassium in cereal. The optional 
&: and
has: contains
or: 
<: less than 
>: greater than 
"==": is or equal to

Examples:
manufacuter == Kelloggs & potassium 

connection function:
could write five functions 

or just query with type paramter, other just informaiton 

A = American Home Food Products;
G = General Mills
K = Kelloggs
N = Nabisco
P = Post
Q = Quaker Oats
R = Ralston Purina
